Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end
if not (gs_shadow) then shadow off
bDetailed = (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2) if bDetailed then resol gs_resol else resol 8 endif
pen gs_cont_pen
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Hotspots ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
unID = 1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -a/2 + radPanel, -b/2 + radPanel, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot a/2 - radPanel, -b/2 + radPanel, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot a/2 - radPanel, b/2 - radPanel, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -a/2 + radPanel, b/2 - radPanel, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1
hotspot -a/2 + radPanel, -b/2 + radPanel, panelThk, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot a/2 - radPanel, -b/2 + radPanel, panelThk, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot a/2 - radPanel, b/2 - radPanel, panelThk, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -a/2 + radPanel, b/2 - radPanel, panelThk, unID : unID = unID + 1
hotspot -gs_boxLength/2, -gs_boxWidth/2, zzyzx, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot gs_boxLength/2, -gs_boxWidth/2, zzyzx, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot gs_boxLength/2, gs_boxWidth/2, zzyzx, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot -gs_boxLength/2, gs_boxWidth/2, zzyzx, unID : unID = unID + 1
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Setting materials for MEP ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if useSysMat then gs_matPanel = sMat gs_matBox = sMat gs_matGrille = sMat gs_matLouvre = sMat endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Panel ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ material gs_matPanel
gosub 100 ! contour coordinates addz panelThk - 0.003 prism_ nsp/3, 0.003, get (nsp) del 1
roofAngleNeeded = 0 for i = 1 to 2 ! 2 holes for louvres gosub 100 + 100 * i
cutpolya nsp/3, 2, 0, get (nsp) next i
gosub 100 ! contour coordinates
addz panelThk - 0.003 mulz -1
if bDetailed then fprism_ gs_matPanel, gs_matPanel, gs_matPanel, gs_matPanel, nsp/3, panelThk - 0.003, 10, min (panelThk - 0.003, panelThk*2/3), get (nsp) else prism_ nsp/3, panelThk - 0.003, get (nsp) endif
del 2
for i = 1 to 2 cutend next i
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Box ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ material gs_matBox addz panelThk prism_ 5, zzyzx - panelThk, -gs_boxLength/2, gs_boxWidth/2, 15, gs_boxLength/2, gs_boxWidth/2, 15, gs_boxLength/2, -gs_boxWidth/2, 15, -gs_boxLength/2, -gs_boxWidth/2, 15, -gs_boxLength/2, gs_boxWidth/2, -1 del 1
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Louvre ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ if bDetailed then roofAngleNeeded = 1
gosub 200 ! top louvre coordinates
croof_ gs_matLouvre, gs_matLouvre, gs_matLouvre, nsp/4, 0, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.01, 1, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.01, 0, 20, louvreThk, get(nsp)
gosub 300 ! bottom louvre coordinates
croof_ gs_matLouvre, gs_matLouvre, gs_matLouvre, nsp/4, 0, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.01, 1, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.01, 0, -20, louvreThk, get(nsp)
endif
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! MEP connections ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
pen gs_cont_pen if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then resol 8 if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then resol 24
call "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" parameters SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = gs_matBox, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 17, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 17, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 17
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Subroutines ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! --- contour coordinates ------------------------------------------------------ 100: put -a/2 + radPanel, -b/2, 14, a/2 - radPanel, -b/2, 14, a/2, -b/2 + radPanel, 1014, a/2, b/2 - radPanel, 14, a/2 - radPanel, b/2, 1014, -a/2 + radPanel, b/2, 14, -a/2, b/2 - radPanel, 1014, -a/2, -b/2 + radPanel, 14, -a/2 + radPanel, -b/2, 1014, -a/2 + radPanel, -b/2, -1 return
! --- top louvre coordinates --------------------------------------------------- 200: put -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.005 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 15 else put 15 endif
put gs_boxLength/2 - 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.005 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 15 else put 15 endif
put gs_boxLength/2 - 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.065 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 1015 else put 1015 endif
put -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.065 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 15 else put 15 endif
put -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.005 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 1015 else put 1015 endif return
! --- bottom louvre coordinates ------------------------------------------------ 300: put -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.005 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 15 else put 15 endif
put gs_boxLength/2 - 0.035, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.005 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 15 else put 15 endif
put gs_boxLength/2 - 0.035, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.065 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 1015 else put 1015 endif
put -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.065 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 15 else put 15 endif
put -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, -gs_boxWidth/2 + 0.005 if roofAngleNeeded then put 0, 1015 else put 1015 endif return

poly2_b 5, 1+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.005, 1, gs_boxLength/2 - 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.005, 1, gs_boxLength/2 - 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.065, 1001, -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.065, 1, -gs_boxLength/2 + 0.035, gs_boxWidth/2 - 0.005, 1001 endif
pen gs_cont_pen
DrawingNum = 1
call "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" parameters SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 13, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 13, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 13
